<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111542>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Head of Merodon mixtum sp. n.. A, C lateral view, B, D dorsal view. A, B male, C, D female. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111542/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111544>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Male of Merodon mixtum sp. n.. A dorsal view, B lateral view. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111544/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111546>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Legs of male in Merodon mixtum sp. n.. A profemur and protibia, B mesofemur and mesotibia, C metafemur and metatibia, A-C anterior view, D ventral view. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111546/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111548>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Metatrochanter and metafemur of Merodon male, anterior view. A Merodon mixtum sp. n., B Merodon geniculatus Strobl, C Merodon trochantericus, D Merodon trebevicensis Strobl, E Merodon caucasicus. t—thorn on trochanter, bb—basal bulge, cb—central bulge. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111548/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111550>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Abdomen of male. A, B Merodon mixtum sp. n., C Merodon constans (Rossi), D Merodon chrysotrichos. A, C, D dorsal view, B sterna 4, ventral view. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111550/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111552>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Male genitalia of Merodon mixtum sp. n.. A, B epandrium, C hypandrium. A, C lateral view, B ventral view. al— anterior surstyle lobe, pl—posterior surstyle lobe, c—cercus, s—lateral sclerite of aedeagus. Scale bar, 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111552/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111556>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Female of Merodon mixtum sp. n., A habitus, dorsal view, B hind leg, anterior view. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111556/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111558>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Distribution map of Merodon eumerusi sp. n. and Merodon mixtum sp. n. (KG—Kyrgyzstan, TJ—Tajikistan)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111558/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111554>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Male genitalia of Merodon, epandrium, lateral view. A Merodon constans, B Merodon caucasicus, C Merodon albifrons Meigen, D Merodon trochantericus, E Merodon geniculatus, F Merodon ruficornis Meigen. p—thorn-like process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111554/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

